transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Yes sir.
Customer: Nagendra bol raha tha Ujjwal ji baat kar raha hun. Ji ji ji sir bataiye kaise hain aap theek hain sir.
Executive: Ujjwal ji baat kar rahe hain. Haan ji ha ji Ujjwal ji baat kar raha hun main.
Customer: Achcha Ujjwal ji main ye puch raha tha ki aap mujhe ye batayenge ki hume jo hai kitni by lead mil rahi hai abhi sir.
Executive: Bilkul ek minute ruk jaiye bata raha hun main line par rahiyega.

[inaudible]

Customer: Kya hai?
[inaudible]
Customer: Kal milega. Nahi kal nahi payegi.

Customer: Nahi wo bhi chala gaya. Wo kis naam se tha aapka?


Executive: Ji bol raha hun.
Customer: Pandey ke sath hi gayi thi maine subah.

Executive: Sir total aapko jo leads milti hai na wo milti hai 91 leads per week.
Customer: Achcha.
Executive: Ji. Total 91 per week. Haan ji matlab aapko 70 Sorry. Yani ki 364 by lead milti hai. Haan agar 91 into main four kar do four week ke according to aapko 364 leads per month milti hai.
Customer: Achcha ab main abhi by lead consume kitni kari hai jo November mein.
Executive: November mein kitni lead abhi tak aap consume kar chuke ho?
Customer: Haan. Sahi hai sahi hai.

Executive: Abhi aapne November mein jo kari hai wo kari hai 246.
Customer: Ye mujhe kahan show hogi?
Executive: Aap laptop par hain?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Theek hai aap profile ka option par click kariye.
Customer: Ji. Aur wahan par aapko ek option mil raha hoga performance report ka.
Customer: Haan mil gaya. Mil gaya wahan par dekhiye aapko by lead ka bhi option aa raha hoga inquiry ka bhi aa raha hoga calls ka bhi aa raha hoga hai na.
Executive: By lead mein chale gaye hum. Wahan par ab dekhiye per month wise aapko number dikha raha hai na ki aapko aapne kitni lead consume kari hai. Graph bana hai.
Customer: Haan. Theek hai to aap per month wise apna dekh sakte ho ki aapne kitni lead consume kari hai per per month jaise pichle mahine October mein sabse kam lead consume kari hai aapne.
Customer: Achcha. 114 lead aapne 114 lead pichle mahine consume kari hai baki mahine aapne kari hai achchi khasi lead 300 ke upar hi.
Executive: By lead consume 364 June July August September October October mein 114 kari hai. October mein 114. November mein 246 246 ho gayi hai abhi tak. 46 lead abhi tak aapne consume kar li hai. Kal parso aur 31 hai na sorry 30 30 tarikh tak ka jo data banega wo aapko ek tarikh ko mil jayega ki aapko ek tarikh ek pichle mahine aapne kitni lead consume kari hai. Ek Ujjwal ji kuch maine na message karwaya tha kuch ek minute ruk jayega. Ji jo maine aapko message karaya tha review ka ha ha uska aapne kuch bhi nahi kara abhi. Mam wo sir us uske liye na maine detail mangi thi na aapne jo mere ko screenshot bheje the na usme screenshot uska tha ki in in customer ne hume review diya hua hai kharab theek hai lekin unme se kisi bhi customer ki aapne chat mujhe nahi bhej de ki is customer se meri deal bhi nahi hui fir bhi un diya theek hai aur kuch matlab customer ki detail nahi di aapne to main kaise hatwa paunga maine ye cheez bataya bhi tha call karke dobara bhi. Theek hai main madam se bolta hun zara. Aur ek ye jo customer hai na aapka pink ke naam se lekin un customer se baat hi nahi hui na. Tabhi main keh raha hun na bilkul tabhi main keh raha hun to aap mujhe detail bhejoge fir main apni team ko bhejunga ki hamare paas proof hai ki jab supplier se deal hi nahi hui Nagendra ji se deal hi nahi hui to fir inhone review de diya hai to isko hatao to wo log hata denge ab bina proof ke main bhejunga to wo to mere upar hi bolenge na ki bhai kuch document to do. Chalo madam aapse coordinate kar lengi. Theek hai aur ek cheez ye bol raha hun sir Nagendra ji aapke paas mera personal number hai na? Nahi mere paas nahi hai. Sir mera personal number aap abhi main aapko whatsapp message drop kar raha hun apne number se ya fir aap number mera likh lo usko save kar lo aap direct mujhe is number pe call ek bar mera account jo hai na ek bar mera account jo hai sahi se ek bar watch karo ek bar. Theek hai. Kuch dikkat ho rahi hai isme. Kya dikkat aa rahi hai aapko actual kya dikkat samajh mein aa rahi hai? Lead sahi se nahi call kam aa rahi hai. Calls kam aa rahi hai aapke paas? Ek kam karte hain sir ek din mein aa jati thi. Haan. To ek bar please isko jo apne supervision mein leke ek bar free hoke isko dekho ek bar. To aap mujhe batao kab video meeting mein connect kar sakte hain madam ke sath hum ya fir aapke sath. Madam ke sath kar lena aap main bol deta hun abhi aap ek ghante mein kar lena 3 baje. 3 baje main connect karta hun tab tab meeting kar leta hun theek hai aur ye jo aapne abhi jo DID number pe hamare customer ke number pe call kiya hai na isse hamara concern raise ho gaya hai ek to theek hai open ho gaya hai theek hai isko main abhi close kar raha hun aapke paas mail par ek feedback mail aayega us pe yes pe click karke submit kar dijiye. Sir wo to ek bar account account wo to hamari hamari meeting fix ho gayi na sir 3 baje ki meeting to main kar hi lunga chalo main 3 baje ke baad ticket close karunga theek hai. Theek hai theek hai theek hai okay sir okay.

- Calls are coming less.

- Wants review to be removed.

- Informed about total leads per week and month.

- Showed how to check leads consumed per month.

- Executive will coordinate with madam for review removal.

- Meeting scheduled at 3 PM.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will close the ticket after 3 PM.

None
